**Summary:** This documentation describes the Amplitude-Talon.One cohort syncing integration that enables sending user audiences from Amplitude to Talon.One's promotion engine for personalized marketing campaigns with dynamic coupon codes, discounts, and loyalty rewards. The integration has a rate limit of 1000 users per minute and requires mapping Amplitude User IDs to Talon.One Customer Profile IDs.

